sentences.sContent: Tsar Alexander III was on the train into Nice shortly after the line opened in the 1860s. Napoleon III of France followed.
sentences.sContent_eng: Tsar Alexander III was on the train into Nice shortly after the line opened in the 1860s. Napoleon III of France followed.
sentences.sCn: 在这条铁路开通后不久的1860年代，沙皇亚历山大三世乘火车到了尼斯，后面紧跟着法国的拿破仑三世。
